{
  "stem": "8892.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm in line, and I think I'm having soup or something, and a good looking Swedish [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], we called him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He comes-- his name was Gustav too-- and he calls out, Eva Lefkowicz, telegram.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I dropped the plate, and I knew that was from America.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the telegram says, stay where you are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're bringing you out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then from through her, from America getting the corresponding letters-- and I think that was one of the happiest days of my life-- and I opened a letter from her where already my uncle who went before us in Debrecen-- he don't ever even left Hungary.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was just in hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He already contacted, and he found my two brothers came back from labor camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I opened a letter, and the name Bela and Laszlo-- Laci-- and I knew they're alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So and that time, I don't even know if I was able to write to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think so, because Hungary was already occupied by the Russians after that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I just knew that they're alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then later on, my brother, when he went to Israel-- Bela-- he wrote to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I guess, I don't even know through who I got address or what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But already I was in Sweden nine months to get a visa for us to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And of course, my aunt and uncle did not know about my Magda cousin, who was my father's side, the relation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They knew of the family, I mean, they knew the family and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I wrote to them, if she can't come out, then I'm not coming either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came in April 8 to New York, and we came with a luxurious boat, regular visa, regular tickets, in 1946, April.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, immediately.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
